{"title":"数据结构代码实现：循环队列","uid":"2c0eb20e22801903e124c85a889f59a1","slug":"DataStructure-Queue","date":"2020-05-11T13:12:40.000Z","updated":"2020-05-19T14:18:31.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/DataStructure-Queue.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/20200511211349.png","content":"<h2 id=\"循环队列的定义\"><a href=\"#循环队列的定义\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"循环队列的定义\"></a>循环队列的定义</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">#define MaxSize 5\n#define ElemType int\ntypedef struct &#123;\n    ElemType data[MaxSize];\n    int front,rear;\n&#125;SqQueue;</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"初始化队列\"><a href=\"#初始化队列\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"初始化队列\"></a>初始化队列</h2><ul>\n<li>队头和队尾指针为0<br><img src=\"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/20200511211611.png\" alt=\"初始化队列\"><pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">void InitQueue(SqQueue &amp;Q)&#123;\n    Q.front&#x3D;Q.rear&#x3D;0;\n&#125;</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"判断队空\"><a href=\"#判断队空\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"判断队空\"></a>判断队空</h2></li>\n<li>判断队头和队尾指针是否相等<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">bool isEmpty(SqQueue Q)&#123;\n    return Q.rear &#x3D;&#x3D; Q.front;\n&#125;</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"入队操作\"><a href=\"#入队操作\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"入队操作\"></a>入队操作</h2></li>\n<li>判断队满</li>\n<li>没满，则从队尾插入数据，队尾指针加一取模<br><img src=\"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/20200511211613.png\" alt=\"入队操作\"><pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">bool EnQueue(SqQueue &amp;Q,ElemType e)&#123;\n    if((Q.rear+1)%MaxSize&#x3D;&#x3D;Q.front)&#x2F;&#x2F;判断队满\n        return false;\n    Q.data[Q.rear]&#x3D;e;\n    Q.rear&#x3D;(Q.rear+1)%MaxSize;&#x2F;&#x2F;队尾指针加一取模\n    return true;\n&#125;</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"出队操作\"><a href=\"#出队操作\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"出队操作\"></a>出队操作</h2></li>\n<li>判断队空</li>\n<li>非空，则从队头获取出队元素，队头指针加一取模<br><img src=\"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/20200511211615.png\" alt=\"出队操作\"><pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">bool DeQueue(SqQueue &amp;Q,ElemType &amp;e)&#123;\n    if(isEmpty(Q))&#x2F;&#x2F;判断队空\n        return false;\n    e&#x3D;Q.data[Q.front];\n    Q.front&#x3D;(Q.front+1)%MaxSize;&#x2F;&#x2F;队头指针加一取模\n    return true;\n&#125;</code></pre></li>\n</ul>\n","text":"循环队列的定义#define MaxSize 5 #define ElemType int typedef struct &#123; ElemType data[MaxSize]; int front,rear; &#125;SqQueue; 初始化队列 队头和队尾指针为0vo...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":835,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"数据结构","slug":"数据结构","count":11,"path":"api/categories/数据结构.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"数据结构","slug":"数据结构","count":11,"path":"api/tags/数据结构.json"},{"name":"C++","slug":"C","count":11,"path":"api/tags/C.json"},{"name":"考研","slug":"考研","count":11,"path":"api/tags/考研.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%BE%AA%E7%8E%AF%E9%98%9F%E5%88%97%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89\"><span class=\"toc-text\">循环队列的定义</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%88%9D%E5%A7%8B%E5%8C%96%E9%98%9F%E5%88%97\"><span class=\"toc-text\">初始化队列</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%88%A4%E6%96%AD%E9%98%9F%E7%A9%BA\"><span class=\"toc-text\">判断队空</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%85%A5%E9%98%9F%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C\"><span class=\"toc-text\">入队操作</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%87%BA%E9%98%9F%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C\"><span class=\"toc-text\">出队操作</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"CHEN","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/202109161140460.jpg